  |-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
ii: ii (IRC it - filesystem based IRC client)
ii:
ii: ii is a minimalistic FIFO and filesystem based IRC client. It creates
ii: an irc directory tree with server, channel and nick name directories.
ii: In every directory a FIFO file (in) and and normal file (out) is
ii: placed.
ii:
ii: The in file is used to communicate with the servers and the out files
ii: include the server messages. For every channel and every nick name
ii: there will be new in and out files.
ii:
